item.title: About this wiki
item.description: Software This wiki is built with hugo. The syntax highlighting is done by pygments. Modifying the wiki The source files of the wiki are in the notes/content directory of the main repository. All source files are written in markdown with some hugo specific enhancements. If you want to modify the wiki simply modify the markdown files and push to the github repository. On every push the wiki gets build by travis.
